727980f-a.title: Queens: Shore Boulevard - 21st Road
727980f-a.text:
Shore Boulevard, east side, between 21st Road (left),
and 2lst Drive (right) showing the A. D. Ditmar's house, formerly
shingled, but now stuccoed. This hose is on the sit e of the
Daniel Mawrence house which was erected in 1719. In 1852 Dr. Dow
Ditmars was the occupant.
February 9, 1932
P. L. Sperr
